}}'''丙型肝炎病毒'''（Hepatitis C virus，簡稱HCV）<ref>{{Cite web|title=Genus: Hepacivirus|url=https://talk.ictvonline.org/ictv-reports/ictv_online_report/positive-sense-rna-viruses/w/flaviviridae/362/genus-hepacivirus|date=July 2018|publisher=[[國際病毒分類委員會|國際病毒分類委員會]]|accessdate=2020-10-06|archive-date=2020-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200502004559/https://talk.ictvonline.org/ictv-reports/ictv_online_report/positive-sense-rna-viruses/w/flaviviridae/362/genus-hepacivirus|dead-url=no}}</ref>是[[黃病毒科|黃病毒科]]的一种小型（大小为55至65[[纳米|纳米]]）、[[病毒包膜|包膜]]、[[正單鏈RNA病毒|正单链RNA病毒]]。丙型肝炎病毒是[[丙型肝炎|丙型肝炎]]和一些癌症如[[肝癌|肝癌]]（[[肝細胞癌|肝细胞癌]]，简称HCC）和[[淋巴瘤|淋巴瘤]]的病因<ref name="Ferri2015">{{Cite journal|title=HCV syndrome: A constellation of organ- and non-organ specific autoimmune disorders, B-cell non-Hodgkin's lymphoma, and cancer|last=Ferri|first=Clodoveo|journal=World Journal of Hepatology|issue=3|doi=10.4254/wjh.v7.i3.327|year=2015|volume=7|pages=327–43|issn=1948-5182|pmc=4381161|pmid=25848462}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Mechanisms of HCV-induced liver cancer: what did we learn from in vitro and animal studies?|journal=Cancer Lett.|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.canlet.2013.06.028|year=2014|volume=345|pages=210–5|pmc=3844040|pmid=23871966}}</ref>。丙型肝炎病毒可以通過血液传播<ref>{{Cite web|title=丙型肝炎|url=https://www.who.int/zh/news-room/fact-sheets/detail/hepatitis-c|accessdate=|author=世界衛生組織|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2021-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210609010050/https://www.who.int/zh/news-room/fact-sheets/detail/hepatitis-c|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

丙型肝炎病毒由[[哈维·奥尔特|哈维·奥尔特]]、[[迈克尔·霍顿|迈克尔·霍顿]]和[[查尔斯·M·赖斯|查尔斯·M·赖斯]]所發現。三人均在2020年獲得當年的[[诺贝尔生理学或医学奖|诺贝尔生理学或医学奖]]<ref>{{cite news |title=诺贝尔生理学医学奖授予“丙肝”病毒发现者 |url=https://www.dw.com/zh/%E8%AF%BA%E8%B4%9D%E5%B0%94%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E5%8C%BB%E5%AD%A6%E5%A5%96%E6%8E%88%E4%BA%88%E4%B8%99%E8%82%9D%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E8%80%85/a-55162054 |publisher=德國之聲 |accessdate=2020-10-06 |archive-date=2021-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211207233551/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E8%AF%BA%E8%B4%9D%E5%B0%94%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E5%8C%BB%E5%AD%A6%E5%A5%96%E6%8E%88%E4%BA%88%E4%B8%99%E8%82%9D%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E8%80%85/a-55162054 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

